response.original_title: Algún día nos reiremos de esto
response.overview: Hello. Welcome to the channel where I tell my life. Today I am going to tell you an episode that broke my existence. And if you don't mind, I prefer to tell it in the third person, as if I were talking about someone else... because I still need to look at it with a little distance.
response.title: Algún día nos reiremos de esto
